reviewText: not an original film not even close to the original story. not one of my best purchases and very disappointed in this DVD
The worst among all film versions about the story of o.
As a fan of the original book and movie, this version is, in a word, lousy.  Don't waste your money.
This movie wasn't even remotely related to the actual theme of The Story of O, and wasn't clearly marked, it won't play on any of our DVD players, only on the computer.
